{"article_id":"ssNtDOny3vcOEij3","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Jussie Smollett is facing charges again in Chicago","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"stemming from his claim last year","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"that he was the victim of a racist and homophobic attack .","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"The Cook County State ' s Attorney ' s Office confirmed Tuesday","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"that special prosecutor Dan Webb indicted the former Empire star in connection","depth":9},{"id":5,"text":"with making false claims to police .","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"`` As the Cook County State 's Attorney 's Office does in all cases ,","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"the special prosecutor reviewed the facts , evidence , and the law ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"and determined","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"charges were appropriate in this matter .","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"We are unable to comment further","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"as the matter is pending , ''","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"the office tells Yahoo Entertainment in a statement .","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"In March , Smollett was indicted on 16 felony counts of disorderly conduct","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"for making a false report ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"but charges were unexpectedly dropped weeks later .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"City officials ,","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"including Chicago 's mayor ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"were stunned by the decision .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"It prompted a Cook County judge to appoint a special prosecutor","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"to look into the case in August .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Webb 's office released a statement to Chicago 's ABC7 ,","depth":7},{"id":22,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"a Cook County grand jury returned a six-count indictment against Smollett ,","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"charging him with making four separate false reports to Chicago police","depth":14},{"id":25,"text":"`` related to his false claims","depth":15},{"id":26,"text":"that he was the victim of a hate crime ,","depth":15},{"id":27,"text":"knowing","depth":14},{"id":28,"text":"he was not the victim of a crime . '' `` This indictment raises serious questions about the integrity of the investigation","depth":14},{"id":29,"text":"that led to the renewed charges against Mr. Smollett ,","depth":12},{"id":30,"text":"not the least of which is the use of the same CPD detectives","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"who were part of the original investigation into the attack on Mr. Smollett","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"to conduct the current investigation ,","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"despite Mr. Smollett 's pending civil claims against the City of Chicago and CPD officers for malicious prosecution , ''","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"said Tina Glandian .","depth":9},{"id":35,"text":"`` And one of the two witnesses","depth":8},{"id":36,"text":"who testified before the grand jury","depth":8},{"id":37,"text":"is the very same detective","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"Mr. Smollett is currently suing for his role in the initial prosecution of him . ''","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"Glandian continued ,","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"`` After more than five months of investigation , the Office of the Special Prosecutor has not found any evidence of wrongdoing whatsoever","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"related to the dismissal of the charges against Mr. Smollett .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Rather , the charges were appropriately dismissed the first time","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"because they were not supported by the evidence .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"The attempt","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"to re-prosecute Mr. Smollett one year later on the eve of the Cook County State 's Attorney election","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"is clearly all about politics not justice . ''","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Police have claimed all along","depth":5},{"id":48,"text":"that Smollett , with the help of the Osundairo brothers , orchestrated the hate crime in January 2019","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"to further his career .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"The actor ,","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"who is black and gay ,","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"he was jumped by two men","depth":9},{"id":54,"text":"who put a rope around his neck","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"and poured bleach on him .","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"Smollett alleged","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"they shouted homophobic slurs","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"and said","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"he was in `` MAGA country , ''","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"referring to President Donald Trump ' s 2016 campaign slogan `` Make America Great Again . ''","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"The actor has maintained no wrongdoing .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"After charges were dismissed ,","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"the city of Chicago sued Smollett for $ 130,000","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"to recoup investigative costs .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"The 37-year-old countersued","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"alleging","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"he ' s the victim of malicious prosecution .","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"Smollett claimed","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"the false narrative","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"pushed by cops","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"caused him economic harm , `` humiliation , mental anguish and extreme emotional distress . ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Smollett has kept a low-profile over the past year ,","depth":4},{"id":73,"text":"but emerged on social media","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"to defend his character .","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"In October , he replied to someone on Instagram ,","depth":4},{"id":76,"text":"writing ,","depth":5},{"id":77,"text":"`` With all due respect brother ,","depth":8},{"id":78,"text":"y'all can clown me all you want","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"but my story has actually never changed","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and I have n't lied about a thing .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"Y'all can continue to be misinformed , internalized sheep ,","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"who believe","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"what actual proven liars feed you","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"or you can read the actual docs .","depth":9},{"id":85,"text":"Either way , I'mma be alright .","depth":9},{"id":86,"text":"I know me","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"and what happened .","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"You do n't .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"So carry on .","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"All love . ''","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"Want daily pop culture news delivered to your inbox ?","depth":2},{"id":92,"text":"Sign up here for Yahoo Entertainment & Lifestyle 's newsletter .","depth":2}],"relations":[{"parent":185,"left":183,"right":184,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":164,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":164,"left":139,"right":163,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":139,"left":113,"right":138,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":105,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":95,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":95,"left":0,"right":94,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":94,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":97,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":97,"left":3,"right":96,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":96,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":100,"right":102,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":100,"left":6,"right":99,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":99,"left":7,"right":98,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":98,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":102,"left":101,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":101,"left":10,"right":11